{"tid":1857040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年全港口罩普查","createTime":"2020-02-02T03:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T11:50:56.000Z","uid":346958,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"54acd82a0f4ee414ba05a8a00215f95dc8e1d9e7","tid":1857040,"uid":346958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"想邀請大家做個全民口罩普查<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港外科口罩家庭庫存統計 (2/2)</strong><br />\n<strong>Hong Kong Surgical Masks Household Inventory Survey (2/2)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/MfCtskDRXXW6rnz28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FMfCtskDRXXW6rnz28&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=e8712dbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/MfCtskDRXXW6rnz28</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>用意</ins></em><br />\n其實好簡單，<em>想統計下大家手頭上口罩數量</em>。<br />\n呢幾日大家都周圍撲口罩，都知供應係嚴重不足，甚至會長期維持呢個局面。但係，政府除咗唔掌握供應數量，現有口罩數目更加答唔到。<br />\n有見及此，我認為有需要統計下呢個數目，咁樣我哋能夠宏觀同準確咁估計口罩嘅儲量，消耗速度等等一系列有用嘅指標。<br />\n呢件事靠每個人花一分鐘就成事。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>目的</em></ins><br />\n當收集完數據(2/2 23:59)，可以做以下嘅分析<br />\n估算人均口罩存量<br />\n估算平均家庭口罩儲存量<br />\n估算全港口罩數目<br />\n估算人均每日消耗速度<br />\n分析口罩分佈<br />\n等各項指標<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>用途</ins></em><br />\n1. 平均每人/每家庭口罩存量<br />\n可比較自己存貨數量多寡<br />\n2. 全港口罩數目及消耗速度<br />\n可預計未來需求<br />\n3. 口罩分佈情況<br />\n了解口罩集中vs平均分佈<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>注意事項</ins></em><br />\n1. 準確度<br />\n為確保估計準確度，希望大家只係填一次，同埋認真答，因為假嘅數據對件事冇幫助。<br />\n<br />\n2. 匿名回答<br />\n為達至1. 準確度，係要sign in Google先可以填，但係係唔會記錄你嘅email，大家放心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgQhWOa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgQhWOa.png&h=baa74359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 回覆上限問題<br />\n根據呢個post <a href=\"https://support.google.com/docs/thread/14971209?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fdocs%2Fthread%2F14971209%3Fhl%3Den&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=995af152\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/docs/thread/14971209?hl=en</a>，上限約為5,000,000，所以應該冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n4. 不足之處<br />\n由於為第一次調查，問嘅問題唔係盡善盡美，唔能夠解答所有口罩供應分配嘅問題。<br />\n若然有人刻意製造假數據，將會降低調查準確度，所以大家請如實作答。<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>利申</ins></em><br />\n本問卷並無任何商業用途。<br />\n<br />\n請大家快啲填同盡情傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>Previews with dummy data</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLdn8mD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLdn8mD.png&h=ad81bc05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ny5axOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNy5axOi.png&h=a9a1d21d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmDfJUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmDfJUZ.png&h=c429440a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b02fc4060ea354905aa8aae30cea72ed04e4cbf6","tid":1857040,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"快啲同我推上熱門！！<br />\n歡迎自由討論及集氣~<br />\n<br />\n「2020第一波工業行動！」初十醫護大罷工懶人包+線上討論區強勢登場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856987</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2a2893ac7a051c3b7693d005af5c92463de6af4","tid":1857040,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.</span>"},{"pid":"aa5af856d86b37301bb6de58290b6c2bb1a040ac","tid":1857040,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"502396194c4cf269258487aba1ba7a36273e4eb5","tid":1857040,"uid":158355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5af856d86b37301bb6de58290b6c2bb1a040ac","tid":1857040,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03